obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (47564)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title, extent and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47564&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Armed Forces (Punjab`
  line `and Chandigarh) Special Powers Act, 1983.`
  line
  line `(2) It extends to the whole of the State of Punjab and the Union territory of Chandigarh.`
  line
  line `(3) It shall be deemed to have come into force on the 15th day of October, 1983.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (47565)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definitions.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47565&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,—`
  line
  line `(a) "armed forces" means the military forces and the air forces operating as land forces, and`
  line `includes any other armed forces of the Union so operating;`
  line
  line `(b) "disturbed area" means an area which is for the time being declared by notification under`
  line `section 3 to be a disturbed area;`
  line
  line `(c) all other words and expressions used herein, but not defined and defined in the Air Force Act,`
  line `1950 (45 of 1950), or the Army Act, 1950 (46 of 1950), shall have the meanings respectively`
  line `assigned to them in those Acts.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (47566)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Power to declare areas to be disturbed areas.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47566&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `If, in relation to the State of Punjab or the Union`
  line `territory of Chandigarh, the Governor of that State or the Administrator of that Union territory or the`
  line `Central Government, in either case, is of the opinion that the whole or any part of such State or Union`
  line `territory, as the case may be, is in such a disturbed or dangerous condition that the use of armed forces in`
  line `aid of the civil power is necessary, the Governor of the State or the Administrator of that Union territory`
  line `or the Central Government, as the case may be, by notification in the Official Gazette, declare the whole`
  line `or such part of that State or Union territory to be a disturbed area.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (47567)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Special powers of the armed forces.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47567&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `Any commissioned officer, warrant officer,`
  line `non-commissioned officer or any other person of equivalent rank in the armed forces may, in a disturbed`
  line area,—
  line
  line `(a) if he is of opinion that it is necessary so to do for the maintenance of public order, after giving`
  line `such due warning as he may consider necessary, fire upon or otherwise use force, even to the causing`
  line `of death, against any person who is acting in contravention of any law or order for the time being in`
  line `force in the disturbed area prohibiting the assembly of five or more persons or the carrying of`
  line `weapons or of things capable of being used as weapons or of fire-arms, ammunition or explosive`
  line substances;
  line
  line `(b) if he is of opinion that it is necessary so to do, destroy any arms dump, prepared or fortified`
  line `position or shelter from which armed attacks are made or likely to be made or are attempted to be`
  line `made or any structure used as a training camp for armed volunteers or utilised as a hide-out by armed`
  line `gangs or absconders wanted for any offence;`
  line
  line `(c) arrest, without warrant, any person who has committed a cognizable offence or against whom`
  line `a reasonable suspicion exists that he has committed or is about to commit a cognizable offence and`
  line `may use such force as may be necessary to effect the arrest;`
  line
  line `(d) enter and search, without warrant, any premises to make any such arrest as aforesaid or to`
  line `recover any person believed to be wrongfully restrained or confined or any property reasonably`
  line `suspected to be stolen property or any arms, ammunition or explosive substances believed to be`
  line `unlawfully kept in such premises, and may for that purpose use such force as may be necessary, and`
  line `seize any such property, arms, ammunition or explosive substances;`
  line
  line `(e) stop, search and seize any vehicle or vessel reasonably suspected to be carrying any person`
  line `who is a proclaimed offender, or any person who has committed a non-cognizable offence, or againstwhom a reasonable suspicion exists that he has committed or is about to commit a non-cognizable`
  line `offence, or any person who is carrying any arms, ammunition or explosive substance believed to be`
  line `unlawfully held by him and may, for that purpose, use such force as may be necessary to effect such`
  line `stoppage, search or seizure, as the case may be.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (47568)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Power of search to include powers to break open locks, etc.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47568&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `Every person making a search`
  line `under this Act shall have the power to break open the lock of any door, almirah, safe, box, cupboard,`
  line `drawer, package or other thing, if the key thereof is withheld.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (47569)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Arrested person and seized property to be made over to the police.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47569&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `Any person arrested and`
  line `taken into custody under this Act and every property, arm, ammunition or explosive substance or any`
  line `vehicle or vessel seized under this Act, shall be made over to the officer-in-charge of the nearest police`
  line `station with the least possible delay, together with a report of the circumstances occasioning the arrest, or,`
  line `as the case may be, occasioning the seizure of such property, arm, ammunition or explosive substance or`
  line `any vehicle or vessel, as the case may be.`
obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_7:
  sectionId (47570)
  sectionNo (7)
  orderNo 7
  title `Protection of persons acting in good faith under this Act.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_7_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47570&sectionno=7&orderno=7&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_7_content:
  string
  line `No prosecution, suit or other legal`
  line `proceeding shall be instituted, except with the previous sanction of the Central Government, against any`
  line `person in respect of anything done or purported to be done in exercise of the powers conferred by this`
  line Act.
obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_8:
  sectionId (47571)
  sectionNo (8)
  orderNo 8
  title `Repeal and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_8_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561&sectionId=47571&sectionno=8&orderno=8&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00050_198334_1517807326561
obj_root_law_sections_8_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Armed Forces (Punjab and Chandigarh) Special Powers Ordinance,`
  line `1983 (9 of 1983), is hereby repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding such repeal, anything done or any action taken under the said Ordinance shall be`
  line `deemed to have been done or taken under the corresponding provisions of this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes:
  string
  line
